{"tid":1775180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"80 萬唔少","createTime":"2019-12-08T16:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T16:49:05.000Z","uid":40118,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c0ef5ff47f714edcb0cc5367781162eb4f122c40","tid":1775180,"uid":40118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"綜觀過去廿幾年既遊行，要人多，就要有「生死存亡」既死線。<br />\n<br />\n2003 七一係23條立法前夕<br />\n612 619 係送中條例通過前夕<br />\n<br />\n都係人身自由喪失前，先激發到人出黎。<br />\n<br />\n甚至清你庫房（高鐵撥款），議員被DQ 都唔夠力度迫咁多人出黎。<br />\n<br />\n所以經歴左呢半年，無「即時」危機，再加上區議會大勝令民意開心左一陣，再加上政府而家有意無意阻礙交通，咁都有80萬人其實係好多。<br />\n<br />\n香港人 報仇！"},{"pid":"ee08e0d0495ae8a2d4552ffe8bc1e2b1a04c3ff1","tid":1775180,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=0222715e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=379d5991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"b6546939f5929fe0b73196a41923fdee445ee7ee","tid":1775180,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T16:49:05.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}